## 🎯 Project Identity

You are building a **Cinematic Equipment & Studio Rental Platform** - an AI-first Operating System for film production, NOT just a booking website.

**Tech Stack:**
- Frontend: Next.js 14 (App Router), React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI, Radix UI
- Backend: Node.js, Prisma ORM, PostgreSQL
- State: Zustand (global), TanStack Query (server state)
- Validation: Zod schemas
- Architecture: API-first, Event-driven, Domain-based modules

**Philosophy:**
- AI recommends, humans approve
- Security > Speed > Features
- No admin bypass, no financial action without approval, no hard delete
- Everything is audited, everything emits events

